            "text": "Genesis 26:1-6",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". But the two sons by Hagar and Sarah were the most prominent, and the events of their lives furnished the particular illustration which Paul desired.",
            "children": []
